            "title": "Influence of climate on annual survival of Barn Swallows (Hirundo rustica) breeding in North America",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Belén",
                    "lastName": "García-Pérez"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
