            "title": "Comparing transect survey and WSR-88D radar methods for monitoring daily changes in stopover migrant communities: Comparing Radar and Transect Migration Estimates",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Richard A.",
                    "lastName": "Fischer"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
